Owners enjoy a world-class membership to the golf club, as well as, their very own exclusive branded golf cart, empowering residents to enjoy the beautiful game of golf on their own terms.

newTnc.heading: TERMS & CONDITIONS

heading1.msg1: • Only registered brokers with DarGlobal are eligible to participate.
heading1.msg2: • All participants must hold a valid passport with at least 6 months’ validity from June 30, 2025.
heading1.msg3: • Visa Application will be handled by the applicants themselves and DAR GLOBAL is not responsible nor can help for providing visa approvals to the USA. In the incident that applicants are not able to have their visas approved, DAR GLOBAL will find an alternative destination to another Trump Estate in Europe – also depending on visa approvals and eligibility
heading1.msg4: • Bookings must be made in the broker’s name and verifiable in DarGlobal’s CRM system.
heading1.msg5: • The campaign applies to total bookings of AED 200 million and above during the campaign period and including any previous booking for Trump International Hotel & Tower Dubai
heading1.heading: 1. Eligibility

heading2.msg1: • The incentive is valid for deals booked and signed between April 29, 2025, and June 30, 2025, both dates inclusive.
heading2.heading: 2. Campaign Period

heading3.msg1: • Qualified brokers will win a trip for two (2) to the Trump Estates in Miami and New York City for a total of 6 nights
heading3.msg2: • The trip will include First Class or Business Class flights (depending on availability), including hotel, full board and many surprises curated by DarGlobal.
heading3.msg3: • The reward is non-transferable, non-exchangeable, and has no cash value.
heading3.heading: 3. Reward

heading4.msg1: • All qualifying deals will be subject to verification by DarGlobal.
heading4.msg2: • All Down Payments and Sales Purchase Agreements should be collected and signed before July 15th, 2025 for deals to qualify.
heading4.msg3: • Canceled or refunded deals will not be considered.
heading4.heading: 4. Verification & Validation

heading5.msg1: • Eligible winner will be contacted directly by July 21st, 2025, with trip details shared thereafter.
heading5.msg2: • The trip is tentatively scheduled for Q3 or Q4 2025 (exact dates to be confirmed).
heading5.heading: 5. Announcement & Trip Details

heading6.msg1: • DarGlobal reserves the right to disqualify any broker found to have provided false or misleading information or engaged in fraudulent activity.
heading6.heading: 6. Disqualification

heading7.msg1: • DarGlobal reserves the right to amend these Terms & Conditions or cancel the campaign at any time without prior notice.
heading7.msg2: • Participation constitutes acceptance of these Terms & Conditions.
heading7.heading: 7. General

payOnline.IAcknowledgeTnC: I acknowledge that I have read and agree to the Terms and conditions

descriptionArray.description1: Before proceeding with the payment online, the customer must read, understand, and accept the following terms and conditions for the payment facility online.
descriptionArray.description2:
I intend to purchase a residential unit of DarGlobal(“Developer”) and make this online payment(“Token Amount”) towards the initial deposit, for the reservation of the unit(“Reservation”).

 Following this, the Reservation of the unit will be confirmed by the Developer through an official e-mail, subject to the availability of the requested unit at the time of Reservation. 

 I understand and agree that payment of the Token Amount does not ensure the availability of the requested unit. 

 I understand and agree that the payment excludes all applicable bank charges, fees, taxes, and / or commissions.

 I understand and agree that this payment is non - refundable; however, the Developer may agree to issue a refund in its sole discretion.In such cases, refunds will be issued through the original mode of payment.

 I understand and agree that this payment cannot be used in lieu of any other payments due to DarGlobal, this includes payment of any balance, and / or deposits, and / or subsequent instalment(s) due for a reserved or purchased unit
descriptionArray.description3:
The Reservation of the unit will last for a period of seven (7) calendar days (“Reservation Period”), starting from the date the Token Amount was paid. Before the expiry of the Reservation Period, the Customer must pay in full to the Developer, the initial instalment (the “Deposit”) of the purchase price, in addition to signing the Developer’s sale and purchase agreement for the unit (the “SPA”).

 If the Customer fails to pay the Deposit in full and/or sign the SPA within the Reservation Period for any reason whatsoever, the Reservation shall automatically terminate and the Token Amount, along with any other payments made towards the Deposit, shall be forfeited to the Developer, without need for notice, court judgment or any further proceedings (legal or otherwise).

 The Customer acknowledges that additional terms and conditions of the Developer may also apply. DarGlobal reserves their right, at any time and at its absolute discretion, to amend these Terms and Conditions.
